{"tid":2407331,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國SEC專員稱將為比特幣設監管制度","createTime":"2021-02-14T03:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:03:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0636aa4949a3f2770ad9b5ff88c0c57cc2269c","tid":2407331,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕比特幣等加密貨幣近期受到許多大型企業及投資銀行青睞，特斯拉已豪砸數百億加碼，梅隆集團（BNY Mellon Corp）、萬事達卡（Mastercard Inc）及摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）都紛紛表態有意將比特幣加入業務或投資組合行列，這使得美國證券交易委員會（SEC）開始關注加密貨幣，並宣稱需要擬定一個明確的監管制度。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，SEC專員Hester Peirce長期以來一直倡導監管機構制定明確的規則，使加密資產得以蓬勃發展而不必擔心違反法律，因而被加密貨幣愛好者稱為「加密媽媽」。她表示，從GameStop和其他股票的Reddit Rally中得出政策結論還為時過早，但新一代的投資者對此感到很高興。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3439436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3439436&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=3d451bb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3439436&h=01011244\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3439436</a>"},{"pid":"9d59e34f2065c03e1829e7d8d8762c4fc0b69e3f","tid":2407331,"uid":245484,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:17:09.000Z","msg":"D人仲信你個監管就唔撚會買bitcoin而係買美金啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abfe5b798479b170bb4c514ada5d10e03b84ba7","tid":2407331,"uid":244797,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:18:07.000Z","msg":"自己啲貨幣當廁紙印又唔監管下"},{"pid":"a170b144c7a1ae115e285b318bfbfdce7e504f55","tid":2407331,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"比daddy elon 日日出tweet 撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"